      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_F002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_f002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "pages": [
        [
          "涼姉は、ものすごい勢いで吸いついてくる。"
